---
---

<section class="problem-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="problem-content">
      <p class="problem-label">Sound familiar?</p>
      <h2 class="problem-title">You have 100 content ideas.<br/>Zero published.</h2>
      <div class="problem-list">
        <div class="problem-item">
          <span class="problem-icon">😩</span>
          <p>Writing one blog post takes 3 hours. You need five per week.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-item">
          <span class="problem-icon">🔄</span>
          <p>Each platform needs a different format. LinkedIn, Twitter, newsletter, blog — same idea, four rewrites.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-item">
          <span class="problem-icon">📉</span>
          <p>You start strong on Monday. By Thursday, you've posted nothing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="problem-transition">ContentFlow fixes this.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem-section {
    padding: 5rem 0 3rem;
    background: var(--color-light-gray);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .problem-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .problem-label {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .problem-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 1.1rem + 2.92vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .problem-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .problem-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }

  .problem-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .problem-item p {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .problem-transition {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .problem-section {
      padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
